XENONnT 2023 Experiment Attribution
=====================================

This overlay implements the XENONnT experiment WIMP search result from 2023.

Citation
--------
XENON Collaboration, "First Dark Matter Search with Nuclear Recoils from
the XENONnT Experiment," Phys. Rev. Lett. (PRL) 131, 041003 (2023);
arXiv:2303.14729.

Data provenance
---------------
Efficiency tables and background distributions are derived from publicly
available data in the XENONnT paper cited above (XENON Collaboration).

The DDCalc Fortran module implementing this experiment follows the DDCalc
module pattern (Bringmann et al., EPJC 2021, arXiv:2103.04039) and is
authored by the hephaestus DDCalc overlay team.

Status: STUB — efficiency table and Fortran module are placeholders.
Real data arrives at v1.1 overlay publication.
